				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just wondering how long it lasts. I am not sure that is the right way to describe it but what I mean is when I tell the pet to /pet hold and get the text message that he is awaiting my order to attack, what actions reset him to his normal attack mode. 
<br />

<br />
